height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">调整点：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">删除&ldquo;第三条 转让方、受让方经营者需为同一人。 &rdquo;</span></p>",
